WEBVTT

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:08.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:02.540 --> 00:01:07.980
[The Eternal Fragrance] [Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:08.020 --> 00:01:11.140
[Episode 4]

00:01:15.190 --> 00:01:15.940
Xiaobangchui.

00:01:16.750 --> 00:01:17.730
Henceforth,

00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:19.060
Your surname is Jiang,

00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:21.060
Given name Lifei.

00:01:30.110 --> 00:01:30.730
Jiang

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:32.140
Li

00:01:33.160 --> 00:01:33.780
Fei.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:38.140
At last, I have my own name tag.

00:01:39.110 --> 00:01:39.650
Look,

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:41.500
Jiang Lifei.

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:45.010
Jiang Lifei.

00:01:45.670 --> 00:01:46.730
Such a beautiful name.

00:01:49.030 --> 00:01:51.500
Mr. Zuoqiu is the top cultivator of our era.

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:53.340
He spoke with you alone

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:54.730
And gave you a name.

00:01:55.110 --> 00:01:56.220
Is there some fate binding you two?

00:01:56.270 --> 00:01:57.060
None at all.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:58.450
Truly none?

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:02.140
Your master always hates to trouble himself.

00:02:04.310 --> 00:02:06.730
Does Mr. Zuoqiu know my master?

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:11.780
This chamber pleases me.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:12.620
Name your price.

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:24.300
Don't stay in the same courtyard with His Highness.

00:02:24.710 --> 00:02:26.220
Pack your things and leave!

00:02:26.590 --> 00:02:27.130
Move aside.

00:02:28.670 --> 00:02:29.250
Make way!

00:02:31.550 --> 00:02:33.530
Where are these rabid curs from,

00:02:33.550 --> 00:02:34.500
Without ceasing their noise?

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:37.690
Anyone picking fights shall be expelled from the academy.

00:02:37.710 --> 00:02:38.740
Why waste words on those rabid curs?

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:39.650
Do you wish to be driven out?

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:40.940
Who are you calling a cur?

00:02:41.150 --> 00:02:42.060
Whoever replies is the cur.

00:02:44.430 --> 00:02:45.250
How dare you!

00:02:45.870 --> 00:02:47.340
What are you two idiots waiting for?

00:02:49.320 --> 00:02:50.940
You may fight, but no swords.

00:02:51.110 --> 00:02:51.690
Stop!

00:02:54.430 --> 00:02:54.970
Lanya!

00:02:56.830 --> 00:02:57.530
Your Highness!

00:02:58.360 --> 00:02:59.020
Tongzhou.

00:03:02.870 --> 00:03:03.500
Tongzhou.

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:07.130
Don't believe a word she says.

00:03:07.240 --> 00:03:09.250
I just wanted a room near you,

00:03:09.270 --> 00:03:11.220
So we can take care of each other.

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:19.740
Alright.

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.090
It's my fault again.

00:03:21.670 --> 00:03:22.690
Just you leave.

00:03:22.990 --> 00:03:23.810
Give him the room.

00:03:24.150 --> 00:03:25.530
That's right.

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:28.250
We're classmates by fate; let's get along nicely.

00:03:29.150 --> 00:03:29.690
Come on.

00:03:30.270 --> 00:03:32.740
Let's check out our room.

00:03:36.760 --> 00:03:37.530
Tongzhou,

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:40.020
Let's pick another one.

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:44.410
So annoying!

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.970
Oh, she spotted it.

00:04:43.200 --> 00:04:45.180
This bed is worth a ton of money.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:48.370
Master would love this to bits if he saw it.

00:04:57.150 --> 00:04:58.570
Smells amazing.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:14.100
The academy is such a nice place.

00:05:16.200 --> 00:05:17.370
No wonder they sent me here.

00:05:24.350 --> 00:05:25.420
Old fool,

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:28.890
I got accepted into the academy as you wished.

00:05:30.230 --> 00:05:31.810
But I couldn't find Senior Brother.

00:05:34.350 --> 00:05:36.210
Mr. Zuoqiu seems to know you,

00:05:37.910 --> 00:05:39.130
But he won't say a word.

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:42.010
Everyone around me

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.860
Seems to have secrets.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:06.010
I'll dig out your secret first.

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:14.890
She was always wary of me.

00:06:16.350 --> 00:06:17.860
Now it'll be far harder to draw near her.

00:06:25.790 --> 00:06:27.810
The Soul-destroying Threads trap demons,

00:06:28.760 --> 00:06:31.180
But they'll backfire and ruin your soul and meridians.

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:45.420
She's protected by a seal,

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.130
Plus a fox demon watches over her.

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:53.010
Those threads won't work at all.

00:06:56.440 --> 00:06:57.770
Shanhua is dying.

00:06:58.350 --> 00:06:59.890
To repair his veins and save him,

00:07:00.270 --> 00:07:02.540
We need the Nine-tailed Fox's power.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:04.860
Lei Xiuyuan.

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:19.330
What's up?

00:07:22.520 --> 00:07:23.620
I hurried off this afternoon

00:07:23.880 --> 00:07:24.620
And accidentally grabbed something

00:07:24.640 --> 00:07:25.690
From your bag.

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:30.890
This is yours, right?

00:07:41.830 --> 00:07:43.100
Shanhua's wound can't wait any longer.

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:45.890
I'll risk everything, even my life,

00:07:46.830 --> 00:07:47.860
To try this method.

00:07:51.470 --> 00:07:52.010
It's mine.

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:06.450
You own dozens of masks.

00:08:07.150 --> 00:08:08.570
Which one is the real you?

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:16.570
We don't know each other at all.

00:08:17.640 --> 00:08:19.450
Why keep trying to kill me over and over?

00:08:21.320 --> 00:08:22.420
If you don't tell the truth,

00:08:27.590 --> 00:08:29.250
You'll meet your end tonight.

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:31.740
I stuck around you

00:08:33.110 --> 00:08:34.210
For a reason,

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.300
But I never planned to hurt you.

00:08:38.680 --> 00:08:40.450
My master opened my sea of mind when I was a kid,

00:08:40.920 --> 00:08:43.380
Letting me see all true and false hearts.

00:08:44.510 --> 00:08:46.020
Most of what you said might be real,

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.660
But I definitely spotted

00:08:49.590 --> 00:08:50.610
That hidden hint of malice.

00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:57.380
Who's behind you?

00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:58.450
Spit it out!

00:09:06.510 --> 00:09:07.180
If I talk,

00:09:08.230 --> 00:09:09.610
Shanhua will die.

00:09:11.870 --> 00:09:12.970
It's always Shanhua.

00:09:13.560 --> 00:09:15.330
Why should I care whether he lives or dies?

00:09:20.470 --> 00:09:21.260
I can't tell you,

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:24.210
Or explain why.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:25.900
Otherwise

00:09:31.510 --> 00:09:32.060
Never mind.

00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:35.660
Xiaobangchui

00:09:37.680 --> 00:09:39.140
I did try to kill you.

00:09:40.470 --> 00:09:41.570
Since I can never make amends,

00:09:42.870 --> 00:09:44.260
Let me repay you with my life, okay?

00:09:54.560 --> 00:09:55.420
What are you doing?

00:10:15.350 --> 00:10:16.060
What is this?

00:10:17.110 --> 00:10:17.900
Some cheap pity trick?

00:10:18.710 --> 00:10:19.420
Are you crazy?

00:10:26.200 --> 00:10:27.450
I brought this on myself.

00:10:29.560 --> 00:10:30.420
It has nothing to do with you.

00:10:32.470 --> 00:10:33.210
Leave me alone.

00:10:36.870 --> 00:10:37.570
Lei Xiuyuan,

00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:40.140
Don't think this pitiful trick

00:10:40.680 --> 00:10:41.540
Will make me go easy on you.

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.210
You don't have to.

00:10:47.830 --> 00:10:49.570
I've been on the run from the Longming Sanctuary for seven years,

00:10:50.870 --> 00:10:52.330
Blood covering every step I take.

00:10:55.830 --> 00:10:57.260
I watched Mr. Lu,

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.690
His family and the whole village get massacred,

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:02.420
While I hid underwater

00:11:02.510 --> 00:11:03.420
Just to barely survive.

00:11:04.350 --> 00:11:05.140
All these years,

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.660
I've never slept soundly.

00:11:11.110 --> 00:11:12.420
I'm scared that if I drift off,

00:11:13.510 --> 00:11:14.660
I'll get my head chopped off.

00:11:17.710 --> 00:11:19.090
You always say I'm a curse,

00:11:21.830 --> 00:11:23.260
But you also bring me misfortune.

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:26.610
I can't save Shanhua

00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:29.090
Or bring myself to hurt you.

00:11:31.230 --> 00:11:32.660
I might as well die by your hand.

00:11:50.990 --> 00:11:51.810
You're just rambling

00:11:52.230 --> 00:11:53.210
To make me go easy on you.

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:55.940
Tend your wound by yourself.

00:11:56.990 --> 00:11:57.970
I'm going to look for Bu.

00:11:58.470 --> 00:11:59.140
Hold on.

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:02.140
I knew you had a backup plan.

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:11.850
Take your dagger away.

00:12:13.350 --> 00:12:14.420
Students aren't allowed to fight privately.

00:12:15.870 --> 00:12:16.850
If our teachers catch you,

00:12:18.280 --> 00:12:19.490
You'll get kicked out of the academy.

00:12:31.230 --> 00:12:32.490
If I ignore you, you'll die.

00:12:33.400 --> 00:12:34.610
I never deserved to stay alive anyway.

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:39.090
I've been a burden to Shanhua.

00:12:40.230 --> 00:12:41.300
This life running from danger

00:12:43.830 --> 00:12:44.810
Should end here.

00:12:49.510 --> 00:12:50.660
Hey, stay conscious.

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:55.380
You went way too far with this trick.

00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:56.940
Are you actually ready to die?

00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:12.970
No pulse.

00:13:15.320 --> 00:13:16.260
He's dead for real.

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:22.810
You said

00:13:23.960 --> 00:13:24.810
This wasn't my business.

00:13:31.350 --> 00:13:32.610
But I own this dagger.

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:34.540
They'll check the cut and know right away.

00:13:35.280 --> 00:13:36.780
How am I supposed to clear my name?

00:13:37.280 --> 00:13:38.420
Our teachers aren't blind.

00:13:38.710 --> 00:13:39.660
If they investigate,

00:13:40.110 --> 00:13:43.180
I'll get framed for sure.

00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:46.570
So annoying.

00:13:48.960 --> 00:13:50.260
You've ruined me even up to death.

00:13:50.350 --> 00:13:51.330
I must have been in your debt in my previous life.

00:14:19.630 --> 00:14:21.940
He barely survived amid piles

00:14:22.280 --> 00:14:23.330
Of bodies and endless slaughter.

00:14:24.110 --> 00:14:25.780
Maybe what he told me was genuine.

00:14:33.870 --> 00:14:35.330
People say bad guys live longer,

00:14:35.590 --> 00:14:36.780
So you shouldn't die easily.

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.780
I brought this trouble on myself

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:06.850
And lost terribly.

00:15:43.470 --> 00:15:44.570
As expected, she went easy on me.

00:16:13.960 --> 00:16:14.810
Sleep tight.

00:16:15.160 --> 00:16:16.300
Don't waste my medicine.

00:16:21.870 --> 00:16:23.810
Could it be that Zhenyunzi

00:16:24.280 --> 00:16:25.780
Doesn't give up chasing Riyan,

00:16:27.080 --> 00:16:28.300
And kidnapped Shanhua

00:16:28.320 --> 00:16:29.330
To make Xiuyuan hurt me?

00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:34.690
If you die, everything's over,

00:16:34.990 --> 00:16:36.570
Let alone save your family.

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:40.900
Old man,

00:16:41.590 --> 00:16:43.060
I'll definitely be better than him.

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:45.780
I won't give up.

00:16:47.200 --> 00:16:48.420
I'll track you down.

00:17:38.230 --> 00:17:39.770
I actually fell asleep.

00:17:44.230 --> 00:17:45.180
Quit staring.

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:47.530
These life-saving pills are from my master.

00:17:47.790 --> 00:17:48.580
You're lucky to get to use them.

00:17:54.440 --> 00:17:55.530
You saved my life.

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:01.660
I repaid malice with kindness. That's huge good karma.

00:18:02.310 --> 00:18:03.380
You must repay me.

00:18:15.960 --> 00:18:16.730
Still want to die?

00:18:22.960 --> 00:18:23.660
How about paying me back

00:18:23.680 --> 00:18:24.730
For the pills before you die?

00:18:25.120 --> 00:18:26.180
Stay away as you perish.

00:18:26.200 --> 00:18:27.010
Don't cause me trouble again.

00:18:38.230 --> 00:18:39.490
You'll tear your wound open moving like that.

00:18:40.960 --> 00:18:41.490
Lie back down.

00:18:47.200 --> 00:18:48.420
See? You're bleeding again.

00:18:51.400 --> 00:18:52.730
My medicine is mixed in your blood.

00:18:53.120 --> 00:18:53.820
It's such a waste.

00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:56.340
Alright, whatever.

00:18:57.510 --> 00:18:58.660
Pay for the medicine later.

00:18:59.360 --> 00:19:00.140
Just heal up first.

00:19:03.310 --> 00:19:03.940
Thanks.

00:19:06.600 --> 00:19:07.900
I'll pay you back someday.

00:19:07.920 --> 00:19:08.420
No need.

00:19:10.070 --> 00:19:11.250
We're totally incompatible.

00:19:11.640 --> 00:19:12.970
Someone gets hurt or dies when we get close.

00:19:14.030 --> 00:19:15.340
Better stay away from me later.

00:19:15.710 --> 00:19:16.290
Xiuyuan,

00:19:16.840 --> 00:19:18.010
Why didn't you close the door when you slept?

00:19:18.160 --> 00:19:18.900
What if

00:19:18.990 --> 00:19:19.420
You,

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:22.050
You

00:19:22.600 --> 00:19:24.660
What are you two doing?

00:19:25.510 --> 00:19:26.140
We?

00:19:27.920 --> 00:19:28.530
We talked

00:19:28.960 --> 00:19:30.490
All night by candlelight.

00:19:30.510 --> 00:19:31.620
It got too late, so we slept together

00:19:33.230 --> 00:19:34.140
Slept together?

00:19:35.070 --> 00:19:35.580
What's wrong?

00:19:36.990 --> 00:19:38.210
Nothing's wrong.

00:19:38.990 --> 00:19:40.050
For cultivators like us,

00:19:40.160 --> 00:19:41.290
Sleeping together is totally normal.

00:19:42.920 --> 00:19:44.210
These are the uniforms from the supervisor

00:19:44.440 --> 00:19:45.100
For Xiuyuan.

00:19:49.710 --> 00:19:51.820
Why're you blushing?

00:19:52.360 --> 00:19:54.210
Am, am I blushing?

00:19:55.360 --> 00:19:56.140
Probably just cold.

00:20:03.510 --> 00:20:04.690
This is so pretty!

00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:08.970
I get new clothes too then.

00:20:10.470 --> 00:20:11.050
I'm leaving.

00:20:25.470 --> 00:20:26.530
Let's head over there, Tongzhou.

00:20:26.550 --> 00:20:27.100
Changyue,

00:20:27.470 --> 00:20:28.490
How do I bow properly??

00:20:28.840 --> 00:20:29.820
I think it's like this.

00:20:30.680 --> 00:20:31.450
Left hand.

00:20:31.680 --> 00:20:32.290
Tongzhou,

00:20:32.550 --> 00:20:34.620
We can learn the immortal arts here properly.

00:20:34.790 --> 00:20:36.010
Don't pick fights anymore.

00:20:42.920 --> 00:20:44.180
Look, so gorgeous.

00:21:19.070 --> 00:21:19.530
Gelin!

00:21:20.640 --> 00:21:21.530
Lifei!

00:21:23.960 --> 00:21:24.820
Xiaobangchui?

00:21:35.680 --> 00:21:37.290
We're calling her Lifei from now on.

00:21:37.920 --> 00:21:38.730
Jiang Lifei.

00:21:39.510 --> 00:21:40.580
Even if she wears girls' clothes,

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:43.180
She's still a crafty trickster.

00:21:48.880 --> 00:21:49.900
Whoops, sorry,

00:21:50.120 --> 00:21:51.050
I lost my grip.

00:21:51.120 --> 00:21:51.690
You

00:21:58.270 --> 00:21:58.970
You little

00:22:00.470 --> 00:22:01.340
Quiet down!

00:22:01.920 --> 00:22:03.380
Or you'll be cast out of the academy.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:07.770
Sit down.

00:22:11.680 --> 00:22:13.420
Your teacher, Mr. Hu Jiaping, has something

00:22:13.440 --> 00:22:14.250
To attend to today,

00:22:14.710 --> 00:22:16.100
So he asked me to substitute for him.

00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:20.860
The sword is the king of all weapons.

00:22:21.440 --> 00:22:22.730
So our first class today

00:22:22.840 --> 00:22:24.770
Is sword-flying.

00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:26.900
Walking into the academy,

00:22:26.920 --> 00:22:29.100
You saw the five floating islands around the main hall, huh?

00:22:32.440 --> 00:22:33.690
The cafeteria

00:22:33.710 --> 00:22:35.290
Is on the northernmost one.

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:37.620
Just show your name tag to eat at no cost.

00:22:37.880 --> 00:22:39.860
But if you can't learn to fly,

00:22:39.880 --> 00:22:41.490
You'll get no dinner.

00:22:43.120 --> 00:22:44.050
Can we grab any sword we want?

00:22:45.640 --> 00:22:46.530
What do you think about mine?

00:23:24.840 --> 00:23:25.420
Ye,

00:23:25.790 --> 00:23:26.340
Look,

00:23:27.270 --> 00:23:28.010
I got one too!

00:23:34.200 --> 00:23:35.730
What is this?

00:24:02.070 --> 00:24:04.820
He was badly hurt and can still fly a sword.

00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:06.340
He's unstoppable.

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:16.860
Tongzhou.

00:24:18.550 --> 00:24:19.820
Tongzhou, you did it!

00:24:24.230 --> 00:24:25.660
You're so amazing.

00:24:26.230 --> 00:24:27.210
In such a short time!

00:24:28.600 --> 00:24:29.940
I'm still trying to understand the basics.

00:24:35.070 --> 00:24:36.100
Your Highness,

00:24:36.920 --> 00:24:39.210
We're fellow students for life.

00:24:39.840 --> 00:24:41.100
You can't just let me go

00:24:41.120 --> 00:24:42.420
Without food, right?

00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:50.860
I don't mean to refuse you,

00:24:51.470 --> 00:24:52.730
But you can't draw spirit energy.

00:24:52.960 --> 00:24:53.900
I've got no way to help.

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:56.210
How about lending me

00:24:56.230 --> 00:24:58.250
Some magic pills or treasures?

00:25:01.750 --> 00:25:02.940
Cutting corners only works

00:25:02.960 --> 00:25:04.180
For a moment, not forever.

00:25:04.750 --> 00:25:05.660
Taking shortcuts would disappoint

00:25:06.070 --> 00:25:08.340
Mr. Zuoqiu, who thinks highly of you.

00:25:12.790 --> 00:25:13.660
Lei Xiuyuan.

00:25:22.400 --> 00:25:23.340
Show us how!

00:25:24.710 --> 00:25:27.010
That's the guy who was dying last night?

00:25:27.640 --> 00:25:28.580
I'll say it again.

00:25:28.680 --> 00:25:29.530
Your spirit moves with your mind.

00:25:29.550 --> 00:25:30.250
Match your inhales and exhales.

00:25:30.440 --> 00:25:31.140
Figure it out yourself.

00:25:37.600 --> 00:25:39.210
Tongzhou, catch up to him!

00:25:42.510 --> 00:25:43.900
Cinging so close.

00:25:44.470 --> 00:25:46.620
His Highness really cares about him.

00:26:18.680 --> 00:26:19.250
Lift off.

00:26:29.710 --> 00:26:31.770
I'm going to starve for real.

00:26:34.200 --> 00:26:35.900
I can't summon any spirit energy.

00:26:38.750 --> 00:26:39.900
This is driving me crazy.

00:26:48.840 --> 00:26:50.180
What a big bun.

00:27:12.600 --> 00:27:13.860
Smells so good.

00:27:18.840 --> 00:27:19.970
She still doesn't trust me.

00:27:20.790 --> 00:27:22.900
Pushing too hard will only make things worse.

00:27:31.840 --> 00:27:32.420
Lifei!

00:28:02.990 --> 00:28:03.900
Smells amazing.

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:06.530
I'm actually good at cooking.

00:28:08.030 --> 00:28:08.530
Wait.

00:28:09.070 --> 00:28:10.660
Do you know what fish monster it is?

00:28:10.920 --> 00:28:11.900
How reckless to roast it!

00:28:14.200 --> 00:28:15.050
Who cares what fish it is.

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:16.340
My master said

00:28:16.790 --> 00:28:18.660
Every living thing has a spirit. Don't waste it.

00:28:18.790 --> 00:28:19.860
Eat it to top up my spirit energy.

00:28:27.200 --> 00:28:28.420
Since you saved me,

00:28:29.230 --> 00:28:29.860
Taste first.

00:28:31.750 --> 00:28:32.450
Super fresh.

00:28:34.680 --> 00:28:36.140
You are using me to test the poison!

00:28:42.470 --> 00:28:43.860
You can fly a sword,

00:28:43.960 --> 00:28:44.770
Yet you dare sneak food.

00:28:45.470 --> 00:28:46.140
Your Highness.

00:28:50.230 --> 00:28:50.860
This is for me?

00:28:52.920 --> 00:28:53.620
Let me check.

00:28:59.790 --> 00:29:00.490
What's this?

00:29:03.710 --> 00:29:06.010
I hunted this spirit fish after great trouble.

00:29:06.160 --> 00:29:07.900
Eating it can boost your cultivation and prolong life.

00:29:08.920 --> 00:29:10.490
I made it just for Your Highness.

00:29:13.990 --> 00:29:15.420
It died violently,

00:29:15.440 --> 00:29:16.340
Full of lingering resentment.

00:29:17.030 --> 00:29:18.380
A vengeful ghost might possess you.

00:29:20.270 --> 00:29:20.970
No way.

00:29:21.680 --> 00:29:22.490
You never know.

00:29:25.310 --> 00:29:25.900
It vanished.

00:29:44.550 --> 00:29:45.140
Lifei.

00:30:06.550 --> 00:30:08.690
Weak demon energy, she should be fine.

00:30:09.750 --> 00:30:10.860
We'll check her condition tomorrow morning.

00:30:11.400 --> 00:30:13.450
I'll take her back and watch over her.

00:30:14.710 --> 00:30:15.210
Sit down.

00:30:20.640 --> 00:30:22.010
We're classmates

00:30:22.270 --> 00:30:23.340
And ate fish together,

00:30:24.120 --> 00:30:25.140
I can't just ignore her troubles.

00:30:26.960 --> 00:30:28.180
You lower your status

00:30:28.360 --> 00:30:29.340
To be nice to Lifei.

00:30:30.680 --> 00:30:31.900
Are you using her to win me over?

00:30:34.230 --> 00:30:35.660
If I want to recruit you,

00:30:36.070 --> 00:30:37.250
I wouldn't need to use anyone else.

00:30:44.640 --> 00:30:45.860
You can stay if you're uneasy.

00:30:46.680 --> 00:30:47.690
We'll make do for the night.

00:31:20.280 --> 00:31:21.050
Morning.

00:31:39.480 --> 00:31:40.500
I promise I won't blab.

00:31:41.270 --> 00:31:41.850
Don't worry.

00:31:53.040 --> 00:31:53.820
Morning.

00:32:01.040 --> 00:32:01.890
I'm going back.

00:32:07.640 --> 00:32:08.650
Why rush off?

00:32:08.670 --> 00:32:09.700
You two can keep chatting.

00:32:09.950 --> 00:32:10.500
Wait.

00:32:10.720 --> 00:32:11.420
What to chat about?

00:32:12.720 --> 00:32:13.260
Yeah.

00:32:13.470 --> 00:32:14.700
What's there to talk about?

00:32:19.640 --> 00:32:20.850
Move out of my way!

00:32:20.950 --> 00:32:22.540
How come she's in your room?

00:32:24.640 --> 00:32:25.010
Well.

00:32:25.030 --> 00:32:27.060
What's going on?

00:32:27.310 --> 00:32:27.900
You said

00:32:27.920 --> 00:32:30.500
You hate others entering your room.

00:32:32.750 --> 00:32:34.370
You even shared the bed with her?

00:32:34.750 --> 00:32:36.980
I've never shared a bed with you.

00:32:37.000 --> 00:32:38.140
Why her?

00:32:38.160 --> 00:32:39.090
Not at all.

00:32:40.080 --> 00:32:40.450
Oh.

00:32:40.520 --> 00:32:42.730
Absolutely nothing happened.

00:32:43.000 --> 00:32:44.180
Don't talk nonsense.

00:32:44.440 --> 00:32:45.340
I'll beat you!

00:32:45.360 --> 00:32:48.140
You're so fiery this early in the morning.

00:32:48.160 --> 00:32:49.900
Endless retaliation has no final rest.

00:32:50.000 --> 00:32:51.500
Go. We're leaving.

00:32:52.080 --> 00:32:52.730
See you.

00:32:52.870 --> 00:32:53.650
Let's go!

00:32:54.750 --> 00:32:58.340
My Little Wen,

00:32:59.120 --> 00:33:01.340
I took good care of you for three years,

00:33:01.840 --> 00:33:05.370
Yet you're gone just like that.

00:33:07.190 --> 00:33:08.820
Senior, check it again.

00:33:10.230 --> 00:33:11.820
My Little Wen!

00:33:14.150 --> 00:33:17.170
- I raised it for three years. - Tongzhou,

00:33:17.390 --> 00:33:18.740
Stay away from these two nuisances.

00:33:19.910 --> 00:33:24.020
Can't believe I'm mourning you,

00:33:24.520 --> 00:33:25.930
My little fish today.

00:33:27.950 --> 00:33:28.780
Bu,

00:33:29.430 --> 00:33:30.410
Who died?

00:33:32.800 --> 00:33:34.260
My Little Wen.

00:33:36.630 --> 00:33:38.820
It never hurt anyone,

00:33:39.430 --> 00:33:41.260
But ended up dead like this.

00:33:42.040 --> 00:33:44.340
The heavens are unfair!

00:33:45.390 --> 00:33:48.540
Bu, dead fish can't come back.

00:33:48.880 --> 00:33:49.740
Try not to be too sad.

00:33:50.230 --> 00:33:50.890
My condolences.

00:33:51.600 --> 00:33:52.130
No way.

00:33:53.230 --> 00:33:55.410
Little Wen is a spirit fish that lived for 60 years.

00:33:55.760 --> 00:33:57.450
I'm tracking down the killer to get revenge.

00:34:00.360 --> 00:34:02.970
Little Wen, if you have a spirit,

00:34:04.040 --> 00:34:06.260
Show me who ate you.

00:34:07.040 --> 00:34:07.930
I want to see

00:34:08.200 --> 00:34:09.620
Who had the nerve to do this.

00:34:27.160 --> 00:34:28.620
You killer!

00:34:29.360 --> 00:34:30.010
It's

00:34:32.160 --> 00:34:33.660
You killer!

00:34:38.880 --> 00:34:41.560
[Hu Jiaping, Chufeng Academy]

00:34:45.760 --> 00:34:47.450
I can smell my special spice all over him.

00:34:49.320 --> 00:34:50.780
So it was his doing

00:34:50.800 --> 00:34:52.300
And he stole the fish.

00:34:53.360 --> 00:34:54.340
So infuriating.

00:34:55.430 --> 00:34:56.970
Let's watch Bu give him a hard lesson.

00:35:01.680 --> 00:35:02.620
Mr. Hu,

00:35:04.800 --> 00:35:06.820
Little Wen got eaten by you.

00:35:06.990 --> 00:35:08.570
What a lucky fate for it!

00:35:13.880 --> 00:35:14.370
Wait!

00:35:14.760 --> 00:35:15.370
Bu,

00:35:16.030 --> 00:35:18.050
The fish bones pointed at him.

00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:19.340
He is the killer!

00:35:19.910 --> 00:35:20.450
Shut your mouth!

00:35:21.070 --> 00:35:23.180
This is Mr. Hu Jiaping, the head teacher

00:35:23.200 --> 00:35:24.530
For all your major lessons.

00:35:25.240 --> 00:35:26.340
Mr. Hu

00:35:26.640 --> 00:35:29.660
Is the direct disciple of Immortal Guangwei from Wuyue Court,

00:35:29.680 --> 00:35:32.740
And the strongest cultivation master in this academy.

00:35:33.550 --> 00:35:34.180
Mr. Hu,

00:35:34.550 --> 00:35:36.820
These new students just got here

00:35:36.840 --> 00:35:37.530
And don't know the rules.

00:35:37.990 --> 00:35:38.930
Hope they didn't bother you.

00:35:39.110 --> 00:35:39.890
It's fine.

00:35:40.680 --> 00:35:42.370
Honestly, I didn't know

00:35:42.840 --> 00:35:44.140
Who cooked the fish either.

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:49.090
Bu,

00:35:49.800 --> 00:35:51.530
Since Little Wen had this fate,

00:35:51.760 --> 00:35:53.340
Bury it so it can rest in peace

00:35:53.680 --> 00:35:54.930
In the afterlife.

00:36:18.360 --> 00:36:19.300
It's him.

00:36:22.280 --> 00:36:23.450
Elder Zhu said

00:36:23.800 --> 00:36:25.140
You freshmen

00:36:25.320 --> 00:36:28.370
Have top-tier spirit roots

00:36:28.840 --> 00:36:30.050
And amazing natural talent.

00:36:30.880 --> 00:36:33.300
I want to figure out your strengths

00:36:33.880 --> 00:36:35.620
To tailor teaching for you.

00:36:36.160 --> 00:36:36.970
That's why

00:36:37.360 --> 00:36:38.970
I'm testing your strength today.

00:36:41.360 --> 00:36:44.050
Sir, we've just entered the academy

00:36:44.070 --> 00:36:45.530
And haven't built up our base yet.

00:36:45.880 --> 00:36:47.010
That's exactly

00:36:47.360 --> 00:36:49.090
Why I need to see how strong

00:36:49.430 --> 00:36:50.890
Each of you really is.

00:36:52.240 --> 00:36:52.820
Alright.

00:36:54.390 --> 00:36:57.370
Bring out all your best moves.

00:37:59.320 --> 00:37:59.820
Xiuyuan,

00:38:00.110 --> 00:38:01.140
How did she do that?

00:38:01.430 --> 00:38:01.970
No clue.

00:38:03.510 --> 00:38:04.370
Move aside!

00:38:20.950 --> 00:38:22.090
Your Highness.

00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:46.340
Are you alright?

00:38:52.070 --> 00:38:53.300
With the mediocre aptitude,

00:38:54.160 --> 00:38:55.860
You won't go far.

00:38:58.720 --> 00:38:59.890
Keep training hard.

00:39:09.320 --> 00:39:10.450
I've got pills to protect the heart and meridians.

00:39:11.800 --> 00:39:12.450
Your Highness,

00:39:13.200 --> 00:39:13.700
Well,

00:39:14.880 --> 00:39:15.970
I'm hurt as well.

00:39:21.840 --> 00:39:22.660
Here you are,

00:39:24.550 --> 00:39:25.140
Thanks.

00:39:30.640 --> 00:39:31.180
Lifei,

00:39:33.280 --> 00:39:34.180
I have medicine for you.

00:39:35.240 --> 00:39:36.570
Only Gelin is nice to me,

00:39:37.470 --> 00:39:38.740
Unlike someone else.

00:39:45.990 --> 00:39:47.450
This teacher's really weird.

00:39:47.990 --> 00:39:48.860
Why test our skills

00:39:49.240 --> 00:39:50.620
For no reason?

00:39:52.470 --> 00:39:55.300
Maybe he wants to put us in our place

00:39:55.910 --> 00:39:57.050
And show who's boss.

00:39:58.880 --> 00:39:59.530
Super strange.

00:40:00.550 --> 00:40:01.300
If

00:40:02.320 --> 00:40:03.660
He's our main teacher,

00:40:04.030 --> 00:40:06.140
We'll never catch a break.

00:40:06.640 --> 00:40:07.860
There are loads of teachers here.

00:40:08.680 --> 00:40:10.300
Can we beg Mr. Zuoqiu to replace him?

00:40:10.680 --> 00:40:11.700
Don't even think about it.

00:40:12.110 --> 00:40:13.780
Word has it Mr. Hu

00:40:13.800 --> 00:40:15.530
Has been teaching for three decades.

00:40:15.910 --> 00:40:16.700
He's extremely powerful,

00:40:16.720 --> 00:40:17.860
And the dean thinks highly of him.

00:40:18.110 --> 00:40:19.050
They won't replace him.

00:40:19.430 --> 00:40:20.260
Thirty years?

00:40:25.550 --> 00:40:27.970
He must have met Senior Brother then.

00:40:33.590 --> 00:40:34.300
Mr. Hu.

00:40:37.110 --> 00:40:38.050
What are you doing here?

00:40:38.880 --> 00:40:40.140
You can't even fly a sword,

00:40:40.680 --> 00:40:41.620
Yet you're running around.

00:40:44.070 --> 00:40:45.090
Just finished

00:40:47.280 --> 00:40:48.890
Roasting a bird, fish, and rabbit.

00:40:48.910 --> 00:40:50.450
Flying ones, swimming ones, burrowing ones,

00:40:50.470 --> 00:40:51.370
Everything's here.

00:40:51.950 --> 00:40:53.780
I cooked them just for you.

00:41:06.880 --> 00:41:08.260
Not bad roasting.

00:41:09.360 --> 00:41:09.970
Alright.

00:41:10.720 --> 00:41:11.530
What do you want?

00:41:16.720 --> 00:41:18.660
You've been at the academy for ages.

00:41:19.070 --> 00:41:20.180
Have you ever seen this person?

00:41:22.160 --> 00:41:23.700
Who drew this ugly mess?

00:41:24.680 --> 00:41:25.370
My master.

00:41:26.720 --> 00:41:27.660
My former master,

00:41:27.760 --> 00:41:28.530
Wu Gen.

00:41:36.360 --> 00:41:37.220
Who's the guy in the picture?

00:41:38.390 --> 00:41:39.180
My Senior Brother.

00:41:40.430 --> 00:41:41.340
I heard he's super strong.

00:41:44.360 --> 00:41:48.180
This man with twisted features and triangular eyes

00:41:48.360 --> 00:41:49.340
Is your Senior Brother?

00:41:49.640 --> 00:41:50.140
Yeah.

00:41:50.800 --> 00:41:52.300
Before my master disappeared,

00:41:52.680 --> 00:41:53.860
He told me to find him.

00:41:57.800 --> 00:41:58.570
I'm telling you,

00:41:58.760 --> 00:42:00.340
No such person in our academy.

00:42:00.470 --> 00:42:01.570
Anyone who looks that hideous

00:42:01.590 --> 00:42:03.090
Wouldn't even get through the gate.

00:42:03.110 --> 00:42:03.700
You know?

00:42:04.240 --> 00:42:06.140
Did my master send me here

00:42:06.240 --> 00:42:07.140
On purpose just because

00:42:07.430 --> 00:42:09.220
I'm uninspiring and can't help him?

00:42:11.880 --> 00:42:12.860
If I can't find my Senior Brother,

00:42:13.160 --> 00:42:14.050
I'll train hard by myself

00:42:14.070 --> 00:42:14.890
And track my master down.

00:42:16.280 --> 00:42:17.700
That old man wants to ditch me?

00:42:17.720 --> 00:42:18.300
No way.

00:42:18.470 --> 00:42:19.570
Train hard?

00:42:20.110 --> 00:42:22.890
You're weak all over with mediocre aptitude.

00:42:22.910 --> 00:42:24.140
You can't even fly a sword.

00:42:24.360 --> 00:42:25.260
I'd say

00:42:25.550 --> 00:42:26.860
Don't bother struggling.

00:42:26.990 --> 00:42:28.410
Hard work pays off.

00:42:28.430 --> 00:42:29.260
I'll keep trying.

00:42:30.240 --> 00:42:31.410
Be real with you,

00:42:31.950 --> 00:42:33.660
You're not even fit to be a cultivation furnace.

00:42:34.360 --> 00:42:35.620
How are you going to change your fate?

00:42:38.050 --> 00:42:40.560
[The Eternal Fragrance] [Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:51.800 --> 00:42:55.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

00:42:55.800 --> 00:42:58.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:42:58.560 --> 00:43:01.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

00:43:01.800 --> 00:43:05.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

00:43:05.200 --> 00:43:09.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

00:43:09.360 --> 00:43:12.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

00:43:12.720 --> 00:43:18.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:23.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:43:23.480 --> 00:43:26.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:43:26.360 --> 00:43:28.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:43:28.400 --> 00:43:32.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:43:32.880 --> 00:43:36.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:43:37.080 --> 00:43:40.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:43:40.160 --> 00:43:46.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:43:46.480 --> 00:43:50.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

00:44:03.440 --> 00:44:07.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

00:44:07.400 --> 00:44:10.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:44:10.280 --> 00:44:13.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

00:44:13.680 --> 00:44:17.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

00:44:17.160 --> 00:44:21.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

00:44:21.160 --> 00:44:24.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

00:44:24.600 --> 00:44:30.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

00:44:31.000 --> 00:44:34.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:44:35.200 --> 00:44:37.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:44:38.160 --> 00:44:40.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:44:40.160 --> 00:44:44.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:44:44.600 --> 00:44:48.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:44:48.720 --> 00:44:51.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:44:51.960 --> 00:44:58.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:44:58.720 --> 00:45:02.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

00:45:02.920 --> 00:45:05.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

00:45:05.800 --> 00:45:07.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

00:45:07.880 --> 00:45:12.160
♪Break through the waves, the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

00:45:12.360 --> 00:45:16.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

00:45:16.440 --> 00:45:19.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

00:45:19.600 --> 00:45:25.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

00:45:26.000 --> 00:45:30.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

